data.meta_site_name: Connect North West - Neonatal transport team for the North West
data.text:
We have twenty-five neonatal units in the North West of England and North Wales

Our team looks after the entire of Greater Manchester, the entire of Cheshire & Merseyide, and Cumbria & Lancashire up to Barrow-in-Furness. We also provide out-of-hours support for the transport team in North Wales

All of the twenty-two hospitals within the North West networks, and the three in the North Wales network are listed below. You can see a little bit of information about them, including a contact phone number. If you want to know more about any of them just click the relevant link to be taken to their website

You can take a look at the Connect North West hospitals map on Google. This shows you where each of the hospitals are.

Click “view map” below to be taken to Google
